title: Tigers and Emperors - official
description:
Hello! This is the official torrent for our album. Please read this important message from the band!

We are a band from Brisbane, Australia. Our music is best described as sweet, blusey folk with a touch of rock.

We've put this torrent together after finding other, unauthorised ones. We figure that seeing as the cat is out of the bag, you may as well have the best quality MP3s, with embedded artwork and lyrics!

Is this music free? Well, sort of. It's free to download and listen (hopefully you are doing that right now!), but if you like us and want to keep us, we ask for a small donation via paypal

If you want high quality FLAC downloads, hit us up on Bandcamp. At only $1 a song, it's a bargain! Otherwise, chuck us whatever you feel like.


Also, please have a read of the text on the inside of our CD (the image is included with this download) for more info on our distribution model.

Last of all, drop us a line via our website! We'd love to hear from you, even if you don't want to give us money. Please enjoy our music but for commercial use, it is copyright, all rights reserved.
 
http://www.tigersandemperors.com
